name: Urban Rebel
description:
You ever just... wander around town and want to hop fences and go do mischievous shit with your friends without consequences and be your openly weird fucked up self? Yeah, so do we. Be rebels with us. 
COLLABORATION: Jesse aka 328_lad (on Twitter) is the photographer of the background image taken at Heathcote Valley, NZ 

Drawing on paper, background of the drawing was a clear orange paint glob on paper I used to test paint with. Manipulated in Photoshop for trippy viewing pleasure. You're welcome.
